{"tid":2136467,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"名宿：美斯踢球好過比利馬勒當拿","createTime":"2020-08-02T07:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T03:31:20.000Z","uid":173952,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7aefcabb4a85a320e40c664382e14cb6b201db74","tid":2136467,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T07:25:44.000Z","msg":"阿根廷名宿，87歲的亨伯托-馬斯基奧在採訪中表示，他看過比利（Pel&eacute;）和馬勒當拿（Diego Maradona）踢球，但美斯（Lionel Messi）才是最好的那一個。<br />\n<br />\n  馬斯基奧表示：「我看過迪史堤芬奴、比利、馬勒當拿、告魯夫踢球，但美斯才是最好的。我曾經和他們中的一些人交手過，但我要再強調一遍，美斯才是最棒的那一個。」<br />\n<br />\n  馬斯基奧也承認，另外幾人都是天才：「他們都是自己所在時代偉大的球員，但是現代足球的節奏是不一樣的，你只要看看美斯的入球就瞭解了。美斯在場上的跑動並不多，但當他需要奔跑的時候，皮球就會像粘在他的腳下一樣。」<br />\n<br />\n  「我見過許多偉大的球員有著出色的盤帶技術，但當他們拿到球時，他們的速度都會慢下來，而美斯則恰恰相反，他用一種奇妙的方式做到了盤帶和速度的完美結合。」"},{"pid":"8b784df586c3ed9cc781c317974905d21fc7b143","tid":2136467,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T07:25:57.000Z","msg":"真球王<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da2938dc93aa0634aa9677ab87deea845b3cc72a","tid":2136467,"uid":53855,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T07:32:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://qph.fs.quoracdn.net/main-qimg-c44d54c7677da2c53c27d05fb7187019\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqph.fs.quoracdn.net%2Fmain-qimg-c44d54c7677da2c53c27d05fb7187019&h=6d107382&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美斯: 你哋點幫我講好說話我都係拎唔到嫁.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好增添我壓力啦"},{"pid":"f8306a28527fd8f74112c7d352ab86b50b91e28f","tid":2136467,"uid":173952,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da2938dc93aa0634aa9677ab87deea845b3cc72a","tid":2136467,"uid":53855,"like":7,"dislike":5,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T07:32:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://qph.fs.quoracdn.net/main-qimg-c44d54c7677da2c53c27d05fb7187019\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqph.fs.quoracdn.net%2Fmain-qimg-c44d54c7677da2c53c27d